.idea/
*.sln.iml

## User-specific files
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.DotSettings.user

## Visual Studio
.vs/

## Build results
/bin/
/obj/
**/bin/
**/obj/
artifacts/

## Publish output
publish/
**/publish/

## NuGet
packages/
*.nupkg
project.lock.json
project.assets.json

## Rider / ReSharper
_ReSharper*/
resharper-*/
*.DotSettings

## Dotnet CLI
*.dotnet
*.dotnet/tools

## Logs
*.log

## Backup & Temp files
*.tmp
*.temp
*.cache
*.bak
*.swp

## OS generated files
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

## Visual Studio Code
.vscode/

## Database files
*.db
*.sdf
*.sqlite

## Debug / profiling
*.pdb
*.cachefile

## Deployment
*.publishsettings

## Secret files (uncomment if you keep secrets locally)
# appsettings.*.json
# secrets.json

## Frontend / Node.js (WebStorm)
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.js

## Vite / Build outputs
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/*.local

